Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:23.76,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur4\pos(718,500)}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:23.76,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fad(1000,0)\blur4\pos(972,560)}Pieces of Adam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reports of crustal movement and abnormal weather all over the world!{from ep22}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breaking of the seal on the Legendary Aquarion is affecting the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't contact the Elements, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option is sending the machines we have left to Altair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how? The Dimension Gate is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open a hole through the dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know last time was an accident, and Shrade was there to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, all the holes I've ever dug were pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy W. Hol...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take a risk using your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare oppose me, Wings of the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to secure the true Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the core units! Disable their weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think that'll work, Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the Wings of the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough power to wipe out a Gnis platoon all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send it back at you amplified!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's firing it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just reverse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His power of reversal is canceling out my counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo! You can't have my wench! Not even over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care about that Rare Igura so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my smelly wench! Only mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo, I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Abductor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Mix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo is Altair's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while since it was just us guys in a Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to reach the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done! With a manly Brutal Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how we Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing a hot-blooded Warrior's Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what your body's turned into!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what I used to say, Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holes are dug to bring the world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hole's to bring us to that world you're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll open another great big hole into your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big enough to bury myself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The artificial Dimension Gate has formed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My name is Mixy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix is the pilot of that robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go reverse out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we butted right into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Abductors and the Legendary Aquarion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are the pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne! Is that you, Cayenne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono! What are you doing with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mix's machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two Abductors are trying to get Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Amata and Shrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He played out his final song in the dimensional rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare oppose Sir Izumo as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, Mix! I'm only here to take you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Andy W. Hol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see, Kagura? Don't you care about Altair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This planet can go to hell. I just want my smelly wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight the whole world before I give her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for a single Igura, a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where that voice is calling me from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planet. The land. The life sleeping within.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All are about to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebirth of the Wings of the Sun was a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it divide the world, or reunite it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{cm}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Augmentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this for as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the holes, and Mix'll fill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we came to know each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he keep doing the same pointless move?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why does it feel so familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, I've been waiting so long to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for that now! After you left me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I've felt all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after all this time, you call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I had to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father isn't an Earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Izumo Kamurogi, the commander of Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot afford to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must put an end to the curse of Eve! The Rare Igura's tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father came to Earth on a mission to find a \Nwoman who could withstand interdimensional travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He arrived back when I was an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My machine malfunctioned and I \Ncrashed on Vega. She saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't take me long to realize \NAlicia was the Rare Igura we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took even less time for us to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no position to judge Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost betrayed Altair once myself, for a single woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept her a secret from command, and we returned to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't keep it from Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back some years later. By then, I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he told me about the curse of Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? We don't know what will happen to a Rare Igura there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll help you, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to decide whether I should take you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I was more worried that you would be in danger on a strange, unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought we would be apart for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's just an excuse. I abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to help save my love's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all for the man I loved, the things I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've resented you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hate myself from back then, when all I could do was watch you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were brave enough to go after your love. I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up already, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose! I will not let Alicia's sacrifice go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion is fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Izumo and the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ianthe, created by my mother Oriza!{was this plot ever supposed to go anywhere?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's focusing all of Altair's power into the Ahura Gnis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Altair Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the power of the planet Altair itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a warning shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the true Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll shoot for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAGURA!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the power of the Genesis Infinity Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was all your doing, Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Alicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask you for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took your mother from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're those?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayflies.{this is the "ephemera" thing, I should assume}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only seen them once, when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they went extinct a long time ago when the females died off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Area 337.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where Ianthe has had the most malfunctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Ianthe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother Earth. The goddess of the fertile land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The land that brings forth the blessing of the harvest is symbolized by a feminine figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Male and female. Positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of creation is ordered along these dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From people to lands. From worlds to the universe itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ianthe functioned by drawing energy from the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it took away the mothering power of the land as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of this was because of Ianthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all I have ever done...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Not when we just met!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life meant something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the hope for the two worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the symbol of our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, you need to love too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love the one person more precious to you than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:24:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My destined smelly wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to take all of you and hold you.{mushaburitsuku hard to tl cleanly}
